---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Design Vault - Approachable Design" description="Stop spending hours searching the web for design inspiration. Start with a highly-curated collection of designed sites and never feel stuck again.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-brand-purple text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Design Inspiration</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6">
          The Design Vault
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/70 mb-8">
          A collection of drool-worthy design inspiration
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Stop spending hours searching the web for design inspiration. Start with a highly-curated collection of designed sites and never feel stuck again.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://natekadlac.notion.site/The-Design-Vault-f23e0e4e24c847aca45e0c1ff8e5a3e1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Get Instant Access - $149
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Value Prop -->
      <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/10 mb-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6">
            You need fresh design ideas
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-lg">
            This growing collection will deliver and assist you when you are feeling creatively stuck. Review similar websites and products that match your products or services in seconds.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Features Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Responsive Gallery View</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Browse websites across mobile, tablet, and computer. No account required.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">200+ Sites (Growing to 1,000)</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Extensive database of hand-picked design inspiration, continuously updated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Detailed Metadata</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Service type, domain URL, creator information, and social channel links.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">High-Resolution Screenshots</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Full-page design captures for analysis and measurement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h16a1 1 0 011 1v2.586a1 1 0 01-.293.707l-6.414 6.414a1 1 0 00-.293.707V17l-4 4v-6.586a1 1 0 00-.293-.707L3.293 7.293A1 1 0 013 6.586V4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Smart Filtering</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Organized by tags for easy discovery. Filter by page type and category.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Light & Dark Mode</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60">Browse without burning out your retinas at any time of the day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What's Included -->
      <div class="bg-brand-purple/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-brand-purple/20 mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8 text-center">What's Included</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-coral flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">Immediate lifetime access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-coral flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
